### What the user *Charles* will want to know

`sbank balance statement -u` to see Charles' own balance. Apart from
this one command Charles does not need to know much more about the
slurm bank commands.

If Charles was a PI or Team leader in a project, he may want to see
a more detailed balance sheet. He can do this by `sbank balance
statement`. This will show the usage for all members of all of his
projects.
